<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        a {
            color: black;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: black;
        }

        a:visited {
            color: black;
        }
        #main-screen {
            margin: 70px;
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            #main-screen {
                margin: 45px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            #main-screen {
                margin: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="main-screen">
    <h4>recowrite</h4>
    <div style="text-align: center">
        <h1>Notice of Policy Violation</h1>
    </div>
    <p>Hi there, {{username}}!</p>
    <p>We're reaching out to let you know that we received a report concerning your activity on our platform
        and determined that it violates our community guidelines.</p>
    <p>As a result, a <strong>strike</strong> has been issued to your account.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>More details</h3>
    <dl>
        <dt>Date:</dt>
        <dd>{{date}}</dd>
        <dt>Content:</dt>
        <dd>{{content}}</dd>
        <dt>Reason:</dt>
        <dd>{{reason}}</dd>
    </dl>
    <p>You currently have <strong>{{strikeNr}} out of 3</strong> strikes.</p>
    <p>Keep in mind that once your reach 3 strikes your account will be <strong>permanently terminated</strong>.</p>
    <hr/>
    <h3>What's next?</h3>
    <p>Please review our <a href="">Community Guidelines</a> to ensure that your future posts will comply to our ruleset.
    If you think this is a mistake please do not hesitate to contact us, by replying to this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you for helping us maintain a welcoming and safe platform for everyone.</p>
    <br />
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Best regards,</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0.25rem;"><strong>The recowrite team</strong></p>
    <hr/>
    <div style="text-align: center; color: gray; font-size: smaller">
        <p>Â©{{year}} recowrite</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>